      <title>特朗普上任前，避险情绪推动日本博彩股上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/flight-from-chip-risks-boosts-japan-s-game-stocks-ahead-of-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于科技投资者希望减少对依赖中国的芯片制造设备公司的贸易不确定性的影响，日本游戏股有望成为唐纳德·特朗普当选的意外赢家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/flight-from-chip-risks-boosts-japan-s-game-stocks-ahead-of-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾夫斯谈特朗普与马斯克的“兄弟情”、特斯拉股价、自动驾驶的未来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-17/ives-on-the-trump-musk-bromance-tesla-stock-price-future-of-autonomous-driving</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Wedbush Securities 的 Dan Ives 表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的政府将彻底改变埃隆·马斯克、特斯拉、人工智能和自动驾驶行业。他在“彭博监控”节目中谈到了这一切。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-17/ives-on-the-trump-musk-bromance-tesla-stock-price-future-of-autonomous-driving</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 20:42:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将于未来几天宣布对中国半导体进行调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/biden-to-announce-chinese-semiconductor-probe-in-coming-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登的政府将在未来几天对中国半导体展开贸易调查，此举旨在减少对美国官员认为构成国家安全风险的技术的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/biden-to-announce-chinese-semiconductor-probe-in-coming-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 20:28:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型科技股再次成为纳斯达克 100 指数的“宠儿”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/megacap-tech-stocks-have-gotten-too-big-for-nasdaq-100-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[仅仅一年前，由于规模过大，全球最大的科技公司在纳斯达克 100 指数中的规模被缩减，而本周，当这一著名基准指数进行重新平衡时，这些公司可能又将面临一次缩减。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/megacap-tech-stocks-have-gotten-too-big-for-nasdaq-100-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 20:28:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IDG资本从五角大楼中国名单中被除名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/idg-capital-dropped-from-pentagon-s-china-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国国防部称，在北京和美国设有办事处的风险投资公司IDG资本已被从五角大楼与中国军方有关系的公司名单中剔除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/idg-capital-dropped-from-pentagon-s-china-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 18:28:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究表明北美电网停电风险正在上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/blackout-risk-is-rising-for-north-american-grids-study-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据电网可靠性监管机构的报告，由于电力需求激增和化石燃料发电厂的关闭，未来十年北美大部分地区停电风险将增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/blackout-risk-is-rising-for-north-american-grids-study-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
